title: Sunday Recap of Chenango Forks, Walton, and SV victories
text:
Monday, October 26, 2015 - 1:46:49 AM Local Sports Sunday Recap of Chenango Forks, Walton, and SV victories 10/25/2015 (Updated 10/26/2015 12:22:30 AM) A recap of High School Football from Saturday where #4 Walton beats #5 Harpursville/Afton 36-18 thanks to the defense and running, Chenango Forks continues to win the Chenango Civil War over Valley, and SV's big win over Oneonta to make the playoffs next week.
